code: @Override public ActionRequestValidationException validate() {     ActionRequestValidationException validationException = null.     if (Strings.isNullOrEmpty(queryString)) {         validationException = addValidationError("queryString is missing", validationException).     }     return validationException. }

@Override public String toString() {     return getClass().getSimpleName() + "{" + "realmName='" + realmName + '\'' + ", assertionConsumerServiceURL='" + assertionConsumerServiceURL + '\'' + ", url-query=" + queryString.length() + " chars" + '}'. }
